Sign into root account and insall pkg and sudo with ("pkg install sudo") add user to the sudo group with ("visudo") type ("username ALL=(ALL:ALL) ALL")
Sign into user account and install git with ("sudo pkg install git") the clone this repo with ("git clone https://github.com/Cinnamon3D/Wayland-FreeBSD")
Make script excicutible with ("chmod +x" Fallowed by the .sh script) then run the script with ("bash ./" Fallowed by the .sh script)
